opinion:
548 U.S. 928 (2006)

LENZ
v.
KELLY, WARDEN.

No. 06-5331 (06A64).

Supreme Court of United States.

July 27, 2006.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented *929 to THE CHIEF JUSTICE, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Certiorari denied. JUSTICE STEVENS and JUSTICE GlNSBURG would grant the application for stay of execution.
